// ŸÖŸÉŸàŸÜ ŸÜÿßŸÅÿ∞ÿ© ÿπÿ±ÿ∂ ÿ™ŸÅÿßÿµŸäŸÑ ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±
const RentalDetailsModal = ({ rental, onClose }) => {
  if (!rental) return null;
  
  const formatEgyptDateTime = (dateString) => {
    try {
      if (!dateString) return '--/--/---- --:--:--';
      
      const date = new Date(dateString);
      const egyptDate = new Date(date.toLocaleString("en-US", {timeZone: "Africa/Cairo"}));
      
      const day = egyptDate.getDate().toString().padStart(2, '0');
      const month = (egyptDate.getMonth() + 1).toString().padStart(2, '0');
      const year = egyptDate.getFullYear();
      const hours = egyptDate.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0');
      const minutes = egyptDate.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');
      
      return `${day}/${month}/${year} ${hours}:${minutes}`;
    } catch (error) {
      return '--/--/---- --:--:--';
    }
  };

  const formatDuration = (minutes) => {
    if (!minutes || minutes === 0) return 'ŸàŸÇÿ™ ŸÖŸÅÿ™Ÿàÿ≠';
    if (minutes < 60) return `${minutes} ÿØŸÇŸäŸÇÿ©`;

    const hours = Math.floor(minutes / 60);
    const remainingMinutes = minutes % 60;

    return `${hours} ÿ≥ÿßÿπÿ©${
      remainingMinutes > 0 ? ` ${remainingMinutes} ÿØŸÇŸäŸÇÿ©` : ''
    }`;
  };
  
  const isOpenTime = rental.duration_minutes === 0 || rental.is_open_time;
  const isCancelled = rental.status === 'ŸÖŸÑÿ∫Ÿä';
  const isCompleted = rental.status === 'ŸÖŸÉÿ™ŸÖŸÑ';
  const isRefunded = rental.status === 'ŸÖÿ≥ÿ™ÿ±ÿØ';
  
  return (
    <div className="rentals-page-modal-overlay">
      <div className="rentals-page-modal rentals-page-details-modal">
        <div className="rentals-page-modal-header">
          <h2>
            <span className="rentals-page-header-icon">üìã</span>
            ÿ™ŸÅÿßÿµŸäŸÑ ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ± #{rental.rental_number}
          </h2>
          <button onClick={onClose} className="rentals-page-close-btn">‚úï</button>
        </div>
        
        <div className="rentals-page-modal-body">
          <div className="rentals-page-details-grid">
            <div className="rentals-page-details-section">
              <h3 className="rentals-page-details-title">
                <span className="rentals-page-details-icon">üë§</span>
                ŸÖÿπŸÑŸàŸÖÿßÿ™ ÿßŸÑÿπŸÖŸäŸÑ
              </h3>
              <div className="rentals-page-details-row">
                <span className="rentals-page-details-label">ÿßŸÑÿßÿ≥ŸÖ:</span>
                <span className="rentals-page-details-value">{rental.customer_name || 'ÿ∫Ÿäÿ± ŸÖÿπÿ±ŸàŸÅ'}</span>
              </div>
              <div className="rentals-page-details-row">
                <span className="rentals-page-details-label">ÿßŸÑŸáÿßÿ™ŸÅ:</span>
                <span className="rentals-page-details-value">{rental.customer_phone || 'ÿ∫Ÿäÿ± ŸÖÿπÿ±ŸàŸÅ'}</span>
              </div>
